title: Nico Rosberg blames Lewis Hamilton for first-corner incident - Wimbledon Guardian
text:
Nico Rosberg has accused Lewis Hamilton of "extremely aggressive" driving after the the Mercedes pair collided in a frenetic United States Grand Prix. Hamilton sealed his third championship in Austin after Rosberg threw away victory following an unforced error with just seven laps remaining.
 Wimbledon Guardian.
